Cell["Full 7/8-propagator scan (disabled until seed OK)", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"497ebd41-ee81-478d-a10c-8957c64fc0f0"],

Cell["\<\
Optional and slow (~1-3 h). Only run after In[5] reports HiddenRegionQ=True \
with a single generator. This reloads the full Example 03 driver with \
$HRFEx03RunFullTopologyScanQ=True.\
