Cell["Sanity check (smoke tests)", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"6f2bb82f-59e9-4bb5-8af3-d07ff84eceda"],

Cell["\<\
Fast regression on Seed5pt (+ optional slow HyperCrown x11=0). Set \
$HRFSmokeRunSlowQ=True before evaluating for the boundary check. \
ThreeLoopVertex full scan: $HRFSmokeRunVerySlowQ=True (~30+ min).\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"4e785c60-532c-48a6-ba58-0775fe6f1d0f"],

